{
  "chapter": 16,
  "chapter_summary": "萧十一郎在山谷中拆屋备行，暗示要离开。沈璧君明白他是为了让她回到连城璧身边。两人离开山谷，萧十一郎用卖水果的钱雇车送沈璧君。在客栈中，萧十一郎告知已找到连城璧的下落，沈璧君强忍悲痛与他告别。沈璧君拔下连城璧所赠金钗换酒，请萧十一郎最后共饮。萧十一郎醉后高歌狼心歌，倾诉狼的孤独与世人的偏见。沈璧君回到连城璧下榻的客栈，连城璧不问她的去向。赵无极等人指控萧十一郎灭门孟家庄，沈璧君挺身为他辩护，坦言两月来从未离开他。司徒中平仗义执言，认为不应冤枉好人，建议请萧十一郎来当面了解。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "你在想什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "没有，我什么都没有想。",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "你……你为什么要将屋子拆了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 31,
      "line_end": 31
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "既然已没有人住了，为什么不拆？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 33,
      "line_end": 35
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "怎……怎么会没有人住？你……",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 37,
      "line_end": 37
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "我已要走了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 39,
      "line_end": 39
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "走？为什么要走？这里不是你的家么？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 41,
      "line_end": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "我早已告诉过你，我没有家，而且是个天生的贱骨头，在这里呆不上两个月，就想出去惹惹麻烦了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 45,
      "line_end": 47
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "你说的这是真话？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 49,
      "line_end": 49
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "我为什么要说谎？这种日子我本来就过不惯的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 51,
      "line_end": 51
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "这种日子有什么不好？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 53,
      "line_end": 53
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "你认为好的，我未必也认为好，你和我根本就不同，我天生就是个喜欢惹麻烦找刺激的人。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 55,
      "line_end": 57
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "可是我……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 59,
      "line_end": 59
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "你也该走了，该走的人，迟早总是要走的。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 61,
      "line_end": 61
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "我们什么时候走？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 75,
      "line_end": 75
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "现在就走。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 77,
      "line_end": 77
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "好。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 79,
      "line_end": 79
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "想不到今天你也会坐车回来。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 131,
      "line_end": 133
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "这辆车是替你叫来的。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 141,
      "line_end": 143
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "替我……叫来的……",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 145,
      "line_end": 145
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "不错，是替你叫来的，因为这附近的路你都不熟悉。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 149,
      "line_end": 151
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "你……是不是已找到他了？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 159,
      "line_end": 159
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 161,
      "line_end": 161
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "他在哪里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 171,
      "line_end": 171
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "门口那车夫知道地方，他会带你去的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 173,
      "line_end": 173
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "谢谢你。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 175,
      "line_end": 175
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "不必客气，这本是我应该做的事。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 181,
      "line_end": 181
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "你是不是叫车子在外面等着？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 187,
      "line_end": 187
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "是！好在现在时候还早，你还可以赶一大段路，而且……你反正也没有什么行李要收拾。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 189,
      "line_end": 191
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "而且我知道你一定在急着要走的。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 193,
      "line_end": 195
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "是，我已经有很久没有见过他了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 197,
      "line_end": 197
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "好，你快走吧！以后我们说不定还有见面的机会。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 199,
      "line_end": 199
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "你还有一段路要走，我不再耽误你了，再见吧。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 207,
      "line_end": 209
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "不错，我还有很长的一段路要走，你……你是不是也要走了？",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 211,
      "line_end": 213
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "是，一个人只要活着，就得不停的走。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 215,
      "line_end": 215
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "我还想做一件事，不知道你答不答应？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 217,
      "line_end": 219
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "什么事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 221,
      "line_end": 221
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "我……我想请你喝酒。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 223,
      "line_end": 223
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "是我请你，不是你请我，不说别的，只说你天天都在请我，让我回请一次也是应该的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 225,
      "line_end": 227
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "可是你……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 229,
      "line_end": 229
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "我虽然囊空如洗，但这东西至少还可以换几坛酒，是不是？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 231,
      "line_end": 233
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "你知道，只要有酒喝，我从来也没法子拒绝的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 249,
      "line_end": 251
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "这首歌我已听过许多次，却始终不知道这首歌究竟是什么意思？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 273,
      "line_end": 275
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "你真想知道？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 277,
      "line_end": 279
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "真的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 281,
      "line_end": 281
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "你听不懂，只因这本是首关外蒙人唱的牧歌，但你若听懂了这首歌的意思，恐怕以后就永远再也不想听了。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 283,
      "line_end": 285
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 287,
      "line_end": 287
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "因为这首歌的意思，绝不会被你们这种人所能了解，所能欣赏的。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 289,
      "line_end": 291
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "也许……也许我和别的人有些不同呢？",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 293,
      "line_end": 293
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "好，我说，你听……",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 295,
      "line_end": 295
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "这首歌的意思是说，世人只知道可怜羊，同情羊，绝少会有人知道狼的痛苦、狼的寂寞，世人只看到狼在吃羊时的残忍，却看不到它忍受着孤独和饥饿，在冰天雪地中流浪的情况，羊饿了该吃草，狼饿了呢？难道就该饿死吗？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 297,
      "line_end": 299
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "我问你，你若在寒风刺骨的冰雪荒原上流浪了很多天，滴水未沾，粒米未进，你若看到了一条羊，你会不会吃它？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 303,
      "line_end": 305
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "我醉欲眠君且去！你走吧……快走吧，既然迟早都要走，不如早些走，免得别人赶你……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 319,
      "line_end": 319
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "你回来了？",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 397,
      "line_end": 397
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "text": "是，我回来了。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 399,
      "line_end": 399
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "你没有回来之前，我们本来在商量着一件事。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 429,
      "line_end": 431
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无极",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "嫂夫人总该知道，男人们都是馋嘴，无论商量什么事的时候，都少不了要吃点什么，酒更是万万不可少的。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 433,
      "line_end": 435
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "我知道。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 437,
      "line_end": 437
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无极",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "嫂夫人知道我们在商量的是什么事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 439,
      "line_end": 439
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "我怎会知道！",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 441,
      "line_end": 441
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无极",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "这地方有位孟三爷，不知道嫂夫人可曾听说过？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 459,
      "line_end": 459
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "我认得的人很少。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 461,
      "line_end": 461
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无极",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "这位孟三爷仗义疏财，不下古之孟尝，谁知十多天以前，孟家庄竟被人洗劫一空，家里大大小小一百多口人，不分男女，全都被人杀得干干净净！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 463,
      "line_end": 465
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "不知道这是谁下的毒手？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 467,
      "line_end": 467
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无极",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "自然是大盗萧十一郎！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 469,
      "line_end": 469
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "你是说萧十一郎？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 471,
      "line_end": 471
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无极",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "不错！除了萧十一郎外，还有谁的心这么黑？手这么辣？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 473,
      "line_end": 475
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "孟家庄既已没有活口，又怎知下手的人必定是他？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 477,
      "line_end": 479
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无极",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "萧十一郎不但心黑手辣，而且目中无人，每次做案后，都故意留下自己的姓名……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 481,
      "line_end": 481
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不可能！下这毒手的绝不可能是萧十一郎！你们都冤枉了他，他绝不是你们想像中那样的人！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 483,
      "line_end": 487
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无极",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "嫂夫人心地善良，难免会将坏人也当做好人。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 489,
      "line_end": 491
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_gang",
      "speaker_name": "厉刚",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "但嫂夫人又怎知下这毒手的绝不是他呢？",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 493,
      "line_end": 495
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我知道他绝不可能在这里杀人，因为这两个月来，我从未离开过他！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 501,
      "line_end": 503
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这件事只怕是我们误会了，我相信内人说的话绝不会假。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 513,
      "line_end": 515
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_xiao_tian",
      "speaker_name": "屠啸天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "一定是误会了，一定……",
      "tone": "喃喃",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 519,
      "line_end": 519
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无极",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "嫂夫人旅途劳顿，在下等先告辞，明日再为嫂夫人接风。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 521,
      "line_end": 523
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_tu_zhong_ping",
      "speaker_name": "司徒中平",
      "listener": "char_li_gang",
      "text": "厉兄且慢走一步。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 529,
      "line_end": 529
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_tu_zhong_ping",
      "speaker_name": "司徒中平",
      "listener": "char_li_gang",
      "text": "这件事若不是萧十一郎做的，别的事就也可能都不是他做的，这次我们冤枉了他，别的事也可能冤枉了他。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 535,
      "line_end": 537
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_tu_zhong_ping",
      "speaker_name": "司徒中平",
      "listener": "char_li_gang",
      "text": "你我既然自命为侠义之辈，做的事就不能违背了这侠义二字，宁可放过一千个恶徒，也绝不能冤枉了一个好人。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 547,
      "line_end": 549
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_tu_zhong_ping",
      "speaker_name": "司徒中平",
      "listener": "char_li_gang",
      "text": "常言道：千夫所指，无疾而终。一个人若是受了冤枉无法辩白，那滋味实在比死还要难受。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 551,
      "line_end": 555
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_tu_zhong_ping",
      "speaker_name": "司徒中平",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "萧十一郎若真的不是传说中的那种恶徒，我们非但不能冤枉他，还得想法子替他辩白，洗刷他的污名，让他可以好好的做人。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 563,
      "line_end": 565
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_tu_zhong_ping",
      "speaker_name": "司徒中平",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "但人心难测，一个人究竟是善是恶，也许并不是短短三两个月中就可以看得出的。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 567,
      "line_end": 569
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_si_tu_zhong_ping",
      "text": "但我却可以保证，他绝不是个坏人。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 571,
      "line_end": 571
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_si_tu_zhong_ping",
      "text": "这两个月来，我对他了解得很多，尤其是他三番两次的救我，对我还是一无所求，一听到你们的消息，就立刻将我送到这里来……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 573,
      "line_end": 575
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_tu_zhong_ping",
      "speaker_name": "司徒中平",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "既然如此，嫂夫人也该设法洗刷他的污名才是。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 577,
      "line_end": 577
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_si_tu_zhong_ping",
      "text": "他对我的恩情，我本来以为永远也无法报答，只要能洗清他的污名，让他能重新做人，无论什么事我都愿意做的。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 579,
      "line_end": 581
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_tu_zhong_ping",
      "speaker_name": "司徒中平",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "不知嫂夫人是什么时候跟他分手的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 583,
      "line_end": 583
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_si_tu_zhong_ping",
      "text": "就在今天戌时以后。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 585,
      "line_end": 585
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_tu_zhong_ping",
      "speaker_name": "司徒中平",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "那么，他想必还在附近？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 587,
      "line_end": 587
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_si_tu_zhong_ping",
      "text": "嗯。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 589,
      "line_end": 589
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_tu_zhong_ping",
      "speaker_name": "司徒中平",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "依我之见，嫂夫人最好能将他请到这里来，让我们看看他究竟是个怎么样的人，对他多了解一些。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 591,
      "line_end": 593
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_tu_zhong_ping",
      "speaker_name": "司徒中平",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "萧十一郎的大名，我们已听得多了，但他的人，至今却还没有人见过。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 595,
      "line_end": 597
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_si_tu_zhong_ping",
      "text": "你们若是看见他，就一定可以看出他是怎么样的一个人了，只不过……",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 599,
      "line_end": 601
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_si_tu_zhong_ping",
      "text": "今天却不行。",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 601,
      "line_end": 601
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_tu_zhong_ping",
      "speaker_name": "司徒中平",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 603,
      "line_end": 603
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_si_tu_zhong_ping",
      "text": "今天……他已经醉了，连话都已说不清楚。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 605,
      "line_end": 605
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_tu_zhong_ping",
      "speaker_name": "司徒中平",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "他常醉么？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 607,
      "line_end": 607
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_si_tu_zhong_ping",
      "text": "常醉。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 609,
      "line_end": 609
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_tu_zhong_ping",
      "speaker_name": "司徒中平",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "常喝醉的人，酒量一定不错，而且一定是个直心肠的人，几时若有机会，我倒想跟他喝几杯。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 611,
      "line_end": 613
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_si_tu_zhong_ping",
      "text": "总镖头有河海之量，天下皆知，无论喝了多少，还是稳如泰山，只不过，我看他也未必会输给你。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 615,
      "line_end": 617
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_tu_zhong_ping",
      "speaker_name": "司徒中平",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "哦？他今天喝了多少？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 619,
      "line_end": 619
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_si_tu_zhong_ping",
      "text": "大概最少也有十来斤。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 621,
      "line_end": 621
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_tu_zhong_ping",
      "speaker_name": "司徒中平",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "能喝十来斤的，已可算是好酒量了，但还得看他是在什么地方喝的酒？喝的是什么酒？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 623,
      "line_end": 625
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_tu_zhong_ping",
      "speaker_name": "司徒中平",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "一个人酒量的强弱，和天时、地利、人和，都有关系。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 627,
      "line_end": 629
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_si_tu_zhong_ping",
      "text": "喝酒的地方并不好，就在城外山脚下的一家小客栈，喝的也不是什么好酒，只不过是普通的烧刀子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 631,
      "line_end": 633
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_tu_zhong_ping",
      "speaker_name": "司徒中平",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "如此说来，他酒量果然不错，我倒更想见见他了，只不过……",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 635,
      "line_end": 637
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_tu_zhong_ping",
      "speaker_name": "司徒中平",
      "listener": "char_li_gang",
      "text": "今日天时已晚，好在这事也不急，等嫂夫人安歇过了，再去请他来也不迟……此刻在下若还不走，就当真是不知趣了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 637,
      "line_end": 639
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_tu_zhong_ping",
      "speaker_name": "司徒中平",
      "listener": "char_li_gang",
      "text": "方才那番话，又引动了我的酒兴，不知厉兄可有兴趣陪我再喝两杯去？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 641,
      "line_end": 643
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_gang",
      "speaker_name": "厉刚",
      "listener": "char_si_tu_zhong_ping",
      "text": "好！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 645,
      "line_end": 645
    }
  ],
